query: DELETE u1 FROM users u1 INNER JOIN users u2 ON u1.email = u2.email AND u1.id < u2.id WHERE u1.email IN (SELECT * FROM (SELECT email FROM users GROUP BY email HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) AS t);
